originalText.text:
Analogous has been instrumental from the inception of our organisation, helping us shape our vision, mission, audience and ultimately bringing our brand to life. They constantly help us shape what amazing.community and our conference, Inclusion by Design can be.

amazing.community is indebted to Analogous. They have been with our nonprofit organisation from the very beginning, helping us to shape our mission, our target audience and our branding. Analogous understood from the start what we were trying to do — helped us to vocalize and visualize what amazing.community could be, as well as our Inclusion by Design conference series. The feedback about our brand, website, events and communication has been overwhelmingly positive, helping us achieve our goals as our organisation. It’s an honor working with - and learning from - Fanny and Analogous.
